name: Cave Painting (05/09/2021 - EUREKA)
description: An artwork in the Cave Painting Series by the artist M Plummer-Fernández. This one was created on the 9th of March, 2021, and was the first cave painting to be shared publicly, and has been pinned on Twitter ever since.  It has been enhanced, upscaled, and minted 05/09/2021. The Cave Paintings are produced by a custom neural network system that projects visions onto imaginary caves in response to prompts chosen by the artist.
